tagram 追隨者。該網站經已增加製作「圖像新聞」，以迎合這群新受眾獲取新聞資訊的習慣。<br />\n<br />\n新聞機構近年已意識到作出迅速改變的重要性。當 Facebook 在 2018 年修改貼文排列次序的運算模式，不少新聞機構已改變策略、減少對 Facebook 的依賴。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"澳洲跪左，剛剛睇新聞話佢哋已經改變左法例去遷就Facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467def319882b84815fdfdc56437d818e1c1f78e","tid":2418108,"uid":209255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-56165015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-56165015&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xt2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=c14799ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-56165015&h=2ab2ccb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-56165015</a><br />\n<br />\n俾 Facebook 大巴摑落去"},{"pid":"490bfa73948e813397a77a15df8599c23adb71e2","tid":2418108,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c5e0fbbcd90d942c7e95b3edadb8ff769c0542","tid":2418108,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"fb獨裁政權栽專用"}]}